Class ORIndividualsMatcher

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatcher

    public class ORIndividualsMatcher
extends ORMatcher
    Extension of ORMatcher that represents the instances as networks of individuals, which are added to an in-memory version of the ontology, and that represents queries as anonymous class-expressions.
